OL,6,FA vicar who works with young people
OL,7,Fstruggling with ketamine addiction has
OL,8,Fsaid it is "wiping out young people"
OL,9,Fin Lancashire and across the country.
OL,11,FFather Alex Frost is one of many
OL,12,Fpeople pushing for the drug to be
OL,13,Freclassified from class B to class A.
OL,15,FSome experts say reclassifying
OL,16,Fketamine, known widely as a horse
OL,17,Ftranquilliser, will not act as a
OL,18,Fdeterrent for dealers.
OL,20,FHome Office data estimates 250,000
OL,21,FU.K. adults took the drug last year.
